  ('optician-moex-01269', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '無窮遠處之點狀物體，經一球柱透鏡（spherocylindricallens）折射後，分別在透鏡後方33.33及50.00公分 處形成一水平與一垂直之焦線。此鏡片所形成之最小模糊圈（circleofleastconfusion）位於鏡後幾公分處？', '["16.67公分", "40.00公分", "41.67公分", "83.33公分"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1960c59d2916", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3a7e5b39127c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01270', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '天空的雲看起來是白色的，主要是因為下列何種原因？', '["漫反射", "雷利散射（Rayleighscattering）", "米氏散射（Miescattering）", "折射"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1960c59d2916", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3a7e5b39127c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
